extends layout.pug

block content
  h2 Exclusive Offer for Our Valued Customers

  p Dear #{userName},

  p We're delighted to present you with an exclusive offer designed especially for our valued customers.

  .offer-box(style='background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0; text-align: center;')
    h3(style='color: var(--primary); margin-top: 0;') #{offerTitle}
    p(style='font-size: 18px;') #{offerDescription}
    if offerCode
      p(style='font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 20px; background-color: #f0f0f0; display: inline-block; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px;') #{offerCode}
    if expiryDate
      p(style='margin-top: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;') Valid until: #{expiryDate}

  p To redeem this offer, simply use the code above during checkout on our website or present it when visiting our store.

  p
    a(
      href=websiteUrl,
      target='_blank',
      rel='noopener noreferrer',
      style='display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #4CAF50; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 500;'
    ) Shop Now

  .divider

  p If you have any questions about this offer, please don't hesitate to contact our customer service team. We're always here to assist you.

  p
    strong Glow Cosmetics Team